Marex Financial Hires Govett as Head of Precious Metals

-- B y   A g n i e s z k a   T r o s z k i e w i c z
-- 
2011-05-31T16:50:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/marex-financial-hires-govett-as-head-of-precious-metals-1-.html
Marex Financial Ltd. appointed David
Govett head of precious metals in  London .  Govett will focus on establishing a precious metals
division at Marex, which so far offered bullion trading as part
of its foreign exchange operations, the company said in an e-
mailed statement today. Marex will also have a precious metals
desk in  Hong Kong , it said.  Govett most recently headed precious metals at Tradition
Financial Services in  Australia . He also managed the precious
metals brokerage desks at Cantor Fitzgerald & Co. and ICAP Plc.  The Marex Precious Metals division will be quoting spot,
forwards, futures and options in all precious metals and broking
futures and options on Comex gold and silver and Nymex platinum
and palladium, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Agnieszka Troszkiewicz in London at 
 atroszkiewic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
